Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:10.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:19.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny! Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:53.15,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare die, you old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:57.30,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make Marie sad if you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:01.99,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't like it very much, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:06.37,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take care of the children for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:14.98,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,In any battlefield... the victims \Nwere... always the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:17.64,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It was always the innocent children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:22.90,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I wanted to protect the children
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:28.15,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,that I left the battlefield \Nand became a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:31.52,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:37.28,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,All of you were born sinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:49.88,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing... Sally, look at\Nhow much they've hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:52.13,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Master Licht...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.38,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Rest, my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:56.84,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Valtos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:57.78,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:06.23,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:09.73,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,You belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.23,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I never want to see her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:16.74,main,valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, my lord. All this\N because I let her go alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.99,main,valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined all of this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:23.53,main,licht,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to feel responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:28.12,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they used some underhanded methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling underhanded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:33.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what you did to all \Nthose innocent children!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:40.05,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,She mentioned earlier that the victims \Non the battlefield are always the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.01,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That is incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:45.51,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The victims are the strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:52.02,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Envied, feared, discriminated \Nagainst, persecuted, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.64,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,stolen from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:57.03,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:01.73,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That is why we will not \Nforgive the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:07.91,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we will destroy you \Nand create our own kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:10.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you even talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who attacked first, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.38,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your filthy mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.64,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.64,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Why does someone like you have that grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:30.80,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:34.15,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I can't see his attacks at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.07,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They hit me straight-on \Nat an incredible speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.68,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.55,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:45.17,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If I use my sword as a shield and charge \Nat him, I can avoid a fatal injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.58,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.79,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking that grimoire back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.25,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:03:59.76,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,diâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.60,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:11.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:17.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here? Well, obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:22.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little lost. Give me \Nsome directions, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.80,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Light Magic vs. Dark Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, you were lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, you moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I was joking, dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:11.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're Magic Knights. Of course \Nwe're going to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:18.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone back at the base was useless, \Nso I decided to come myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill them all later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:23.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are they doing when \Nwe're in this much trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:27.32,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He dragged me out of bed, \Nand now we're in this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:31.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, didn't I tell \Nyou to take the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.96,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to give you a permanent vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's his deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he's the leader of \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:47.08,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Eye of the Midnight Sun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:48.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:54.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he'd be some big, burly guy\Nwho could eat a cow in a single gulp,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but he's just a scrawny-ass beanpole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.18,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm pretty sure muscles \Ndon't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:04.73,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy's creepy, \Ninfinite amount of magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.76,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, he uses light magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.94,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's a super rare magic \Nthat only a few people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.86,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,throughout the history of the \NClover Kingdom have ever used!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:16.87,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, he's super \Ndangerous! I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.37,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Black Bulls' captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.80,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I summon the Third Eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:23.63,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:29.92,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to fight him,\Nsince he uses dark magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral, please get the kids and \Neveryone else back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:47.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get a chance to see Captain Yami \Nin action! There's no way I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:51.45,main,finral,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche and, uh... you there! Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.95,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, get to \Nthe old hag! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.83,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I've been around longer than you, y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:02.25,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Yami. I'm leaving the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You better come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.44,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:09.92,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to just \Nstay out of harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:14.17,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I think I'm running low on magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.76,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Like, for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:19.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? I'm for real, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:24.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The hell do you think \Nyou're doing to my ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.78,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Ride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:34.78,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh! I don't have enough \Nlives to stick around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you, Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.29,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You better come back, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:44.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So cool! How'd you stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.50,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:53.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is a weapon called a "katana" \Nfrom my homeland, the Land of the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And that wasâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:58.59,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Like I have time to explain all this \Nright now. Besides, it's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.60,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light Magic: Light Swords of Conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.23,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He's boosting his physical abilities \Nwith reinforcing magic
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:16.95,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,and cutting my light magic with \Na sword cloaked in dark magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.20,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.37,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,How about this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:34.88,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power of the \Ngreat Magic Knight heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have I met you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:50.48,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I don't know \Nanyone who uses light magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:59.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And what's so fun about all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:09.63,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you a fable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:16.72,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, in a certain village, there lived\Na people with very strong magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:20.72,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They were loved by mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:25.89,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They changed the weather \Nand manipulated ley lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.89,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They had power to rival the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:35.40,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The humans from outside the \Nvillage worshipped them as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:40.76,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,However, gradually, the humans \Ngrew to fear their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.16,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They envied it and wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:49.05,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They tricked them, massacred them,\Nand stole their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:53.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of story was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:55.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What's that got to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Planning to become a bard or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I've got a little story, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:09.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,In a certain place,\Nthere was a pure young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:14.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,His folks were fishermen, and they started \Nsending him out to fish from a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.90,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And then he got shipwrecked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.40,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Augh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.12,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,...and washed ashore in a strange country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.33,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.08,flashback,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,He's wearing grass sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.00,flashback,Guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:40.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Since his race and culture were different, \Nhe went through some nasty stuff there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:41.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:48.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He kicked all their asses and \Nbecame the boss of a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:57.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What'd you think of my response fable?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:00.49,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's half of my life, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:03.03,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! You dare mock Master Licht?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:06.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Your face is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:08.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there lines on your face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're bringing that up now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.17,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He got faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:18.55,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,As a foreigner, I suppose my \Nstory had nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.84,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind stepping off the stage, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.43,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long you can \Navoid a fatal blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:37.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the guy who took out Fuegoleon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:39.90,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:46.73,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Although I laid my plans carefully \Nand had him walk into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:54.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You'd never take down that King \Nof Hardnoses with stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:54.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.67,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Master Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:03.15,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing... He's so frickin' cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:06.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, eh? I'm sure you wouldn't \Nhave been able to win
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,without doing something underhanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.03,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.55,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This time, come right at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:17.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the true power \Nof a Magic Knight Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.16,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brat. Were you watching that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:34.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Now try the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Like I could actually do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:42.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:46.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to do it, so do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:52.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, that really hurts! Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:50.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That'll make you a bigger man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.10,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did he manage to stop \Nall of Master Licht's attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.87,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,he even managed to counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.43,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls' captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.25,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Does his strength actually \Nrival the Wizard King's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:09.26,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So this is dark magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:15.01,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light Recovery Magic: \NHealing Light Particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He can use recovery magic, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen it in person much,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:28.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently, guys loved by \Nmana can use all sorts of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's especially rare for an \Nattack-type to also be able to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.87,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He was actually serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:41.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, really! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not in the middle of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I don't have any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:48.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean the last attack I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying do the thing before that, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:55.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't block attacks that I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:16:00.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain it just this once.\NYou'll have to pay me 500 yuls later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:01.77,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's charging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:05.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I've been able \Nto react to the attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:09.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,is because of something called "ki" \Nfrom back in my homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ki? Not mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:26.84,sign_23343_218_Ki,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(443,1)}Ki
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,People looking at you,\Nthe sound of their breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:20.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,their smell, the motions of their muscles,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.03,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,the vague sense that they're there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:25.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Ki is the blanket term for all of the \Ndifferent types of life energy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,the human body emits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:31.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I read that ki and predicted \Nhis next move, then made mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You've done that before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:37.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:45.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,When I do it, I combine it with \Nmagic and muscle, and fight that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:50.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's like being a magic \Nswordsman or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:54.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Muscles! So that's why your neck's \Nso thick, Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:57.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Like you can talk, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:01.42,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,He has the nerve to converse during a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.91,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,The insolence...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:05.56,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He's just full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.46,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,To think he could keep up \Nwith this speed, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.22,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow him to trouble \Nyou any further, Master Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:17.17,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is impertinent of me,\Nbut would you allow me to assist you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:22.56,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Valtos. You're always so helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:27.65,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, that boy... \NWould you capture him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.40,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You may injure him slightly if need be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:33.90,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,An easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:39.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:43.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:46.96,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing. Practice on that \Nscrawny dude with the slanty eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:50.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! On the scrawny dude \Nwith the slanty eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:53.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's too sudden! Of course I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.16,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Where I come from, we've got this saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:00.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,"A warrior never goes back on his word."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:04.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were going to \Nbecome the Wizard King, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Surpass your limits. Right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.73,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:24.33,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, concentrate... Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:31.84,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Someone with no magic like you \Ncould never stop my attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't stop all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:44.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool me, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:48.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You just reacted to your ears that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:54.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Use all five senses, and sense it \Nwith your whole body, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,With my whole body?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:19:00.49,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You can't just rely \Non your ears or your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:04.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Visualize something halfway between \Ninstinct and a prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:06.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do it right, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.33,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I kinda get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:17.30,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not just my ears, not just my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.60,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I'm just going to reset everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.69,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:32.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:36.94,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Whaâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:56.57,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you actually managed to do it?\NTalk about creepy, you weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:57.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.68,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Valtos...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:09.33,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you... harm Valtos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:16.94,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow people like \Nyou to harm my comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.32,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:23.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's your deal? You're the\Nones who started this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:32.15,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The path this spell traces \Nresembles the motions of a whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:34.28,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Can you predict its movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:44.26,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that whips were used to \Npunish criminals, once upon a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:47.39,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it a perfect fit for you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:51.27,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light Creation Magic: Light Whip of Judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:01.03,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to struggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:06.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:10.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That nutcase has gone ballistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:42.97,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear... I held back most of my magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:45.32,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,but it's all really too fragile...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:48.79,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Both this world and you fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:54.00,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Master Licht!\NYour strength is practically divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:59.46,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,If you felt like it, Master Licht, the Magic \NKnights would be no more than infants!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:03.84,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:42.48,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun... Licht, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a huge forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:46.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you'd expect that \Nfrom a light magic user.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:50.57,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 35: \N"The Light of Judgment."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 35\N\N{\fs18} The Light of Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:53.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Going beyond my limits is my magic!
